column16: Rich Aurilia grounds into double play, third baseman Craig Counsell to second baseman Rickie Weeks to first baseman Prince Fielder.    Pablo Sandoval out at 2nd.
Pablo Sandoval singles on a ground ball to left fielder Ryan Braun.    Fred Lewis to 2nd.
Bengie Molina out on a sacrifice fly to right fielder Corey Hart.    Edgar Renteria scores.
Fred Lewis singles on a ground ball to right fielder Corey Hart.    Edgar Renteria to 3rd.
Edgar Renteria singles on a line drive to right fielder Corey Hart.    Randy Winn scores.  Fielding error by right fielder Corey Hart.
Randy Winn doubles (1) on a line drive to right fielder Corey Hart.
